03:49.506 --> 03:51.248
Oh, to find the relationship, yes.

03:51.288 --> 04:02.364
So if you have been, say you've been in a relationship, you've been dating somebody for a couple months, and you want some clarity about where you stand.

04:03.165 --> 04:09.554
You're gonna have a relationship talk, you're gonna have a DTR conversation, you're gonna define the relationship.

04:09.698 --> 04:13.911
