10:12.322 --> 10:14.866
And everything they are to do is to be set apart.

10:14.886 --> 10:16.690
This is the meaning of holiness.

10:16.710 --> 10:17.832
We talk about a holy nation.

10:17.852 --> 10:20.376
Holiness is that quality of being set apart.

10:21.177 --> 10:26.627
