10:26.667 --> 10:32.978
And in this case, it is special use to be used in service to God and by God.

10:34.210 --> 10:42.541
And so Israel as a priestly kingdom, Israel as a holy nation, they are to live in ways that are markedly different from the nations around them.

10:43.482 --> 10:49.390
They are to represent God to the nations showing God's character through the way that they live.

10:49.430 --> 11:01.906
They are to be God's people, showing that yes, we have honor and respect in family relationships and all other relationships that we are loving to our neighbors.

