11:22.089 --> 11:24.914
This is what God is asking for.

11:24.994 --> 11:39.772
that from these people, he's asking for their exclusive commitment, and he's asking that they not be about themselves, that they live in certain ways before other nations so that the other nations might know who God is.

11:40.252 --> 11:49.223
