12:51.938 --> 12:57.687
when you're living in your house, so nobody sees what you're doing, you are the same person.

12:58.288 --> 13:01.913
We are to live this way of fully committed to the Lord.

13:01.953 --> 13:06.961
Live this way outside for the benefit of those around us.

