21:12.254 --> 21:14.860
The reason that I chose you is because I chose you.

21:14.920 --> 21:17.345
And I chose you because I love you.

21:17.385 --> 21:19.650
Nothing can take that away.

21:19.670 --> 21:23.238
These people are God's people.

21:23.658 --> 21:25.362
