21:30.519 --> 21:37.046
Remember that first very, very first opening part, I am the God who freed you from slavery in Egypt.

21:37.727 --> 21:39.409
And now here are my 10 commandments.

21:39.489 --> 21:41.131
Now here's the book of the covenant.

21:41.391 --> 21:42.732
No, they belong to God.

21:43.213 --> 21:48.098
They are his people, not because of what they do or don't do, but because God has laid claim to them.

21:48.199 --> 21:49.580
