God is our God.

21:51.622 --> 21:54.866
We are his people, not because we have earned it.

21:55.266 --> 22:09.575
not because we have done anything to make God favor us above anybody else, but because God in His grace has chosen us to be a part of this covenant of grace, that it extends to us through Jesus Christ and what He has done.

